类的使用
sample.SetUp

  • 使用SetUp的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    controller
    This is the package for all controller classes There are three controller classes for FXML files in this package.
    sample
    This is the package for main game body Basic model of the pacman game is set up with in this class for performing its functionality.

      This method starter will set up the in-game page of pacman Main.starter(SetUp) This method takes an instance of SetUp as input and generate corresponding game board based on settings sample.SetUp The method will first create a game manager with a base javafx group.
